{"tid":2032611,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「正視聽」唔好再有港島情意結","createTime":"2020-05-24T06:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T09:33:12.000Z","uid":197235,"like":324,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"be0c802cf5b53895de45aa8ce92b0de742b2a134","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">此Post絕對唔係笑去港島既人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2019有好多「靚畫面」係港島出現<br />\n<br />\n但係背後係用幾多<span style=\"color: red;\">鮮血</span>換返黎？<br />\n<br />\n「靚畫面」係換黎好多<span style=\"color: red;\">國際掌聲</span> 無錯就係得<span style=\"color: red;\">掌聲</span><br />\n<br />\n佢地真正幫我地出聲既時候 係我地顯露咗<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反抗意志</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一次又一次與強權說不 反抗再反抗<br />\n<br />\n絕對<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔係</span></span>因為一張<span style=\"color: red;\">百萬人大合照</span><br />\n<br />\n由反送中開始 我深信大家明白 <br />\n<br />\n遊行示威 中共港共唔會理 就連國際都只會已讀不會<br />\n<br />\n2020年你仲想要「靚畫面 」我都算<br />\n<br />\n咁點解要選擇港島呢個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">難走難打難集人易被捕</span></span>既地方<br />\n<br />\n2019我地由港島抗爭 變成 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">九龍 分區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係因為我地知港島唔好打<br />\n<br />\n我希望你地下次可以<span style=\"color: red;\">參考上年</span> 而唔係再零開始<br />\n<br />\n分區/九龍總比港島好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">泛民 黃之峰 唔好因為你地所謂嘅畫面吹捧港島</span><br />\n<br />\n比起要畫面 我更希望大家<span style=\"color: red;\">保存生命 一直抗爭</span><br />\n<br />\n2020年比起畫面 大家更需要<span style=\"color: red;\">意志</span><br />\n<br />\n比國際 比手足 比自己 知我地有<span style=\"color: red;\">反抗既心</span><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">中共攬炒，港人迎戰</span>」<br />\n<br />\n最後希望香港人有自由意志 認清目標"},{"pid":"93bed89acdfbd45e906eff27485655217c4c3c57","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":47,"dislike":4,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"下一次可唔可九龍 多好多地方集人<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以分區 影響更大"},{"pid":"c3c0a38131cc13e4660eb0c3bf1bb74da5f80df7","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35654a8b7a3ccb44e30baf9a9788bed6ccf437b","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:56:57.000Z","msg":"港島情意結不能有<br />\n<br />\n為勝利而思考"},{"pid":"6ef35204406606bb06f606bbeff6a45d24f9a7ea","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:57:44.000Z","msg":"或者最低限度都考慮有無其他地方比港島相對安全"},{"pid":"f564bf858a2e277e08d347a898ef69e0785724ce","tid":2032611,"uid":304769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:59:06.000Z","msg":"前線自己執生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=7a78a799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"e7c7a496cf14cd240adf4b248232de95c59ec126","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"唔係話怕犧牲<br />\n<br />\n最怕咩都未做就比人拉咗"},{"pid":"b564a80bb18ef39c373b52f48e46cc9c7465c8c7","tid":2032611,"uid":306592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e7c7a496cf14cd240adf4b248232de95c59ec126","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"唔係話怕犧牲<br />\n<br />\n最怕咩都未做就比人拉咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"真心 <br />\n<br />\n港島每次都似送羊入虎口"},{"pid":"41b8909f32ca807cf026bb16e07bbff2178f9085","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"唔怕惡法 最怕手足有事<br />\n<br />\n唔怕付出 最怕無機會付出<br />\n<br />\n前線一個都不能少"},{"pid":"08c6d942d8bee5360022b98c11d69308732ccf52","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"我相信因港島 令好多新界手足卻步"},{"pid":"0f13518087705a6309ff1741539e66592e1e6dea","tid":2032611,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji